        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Gas leak check</strong><p>All pipework and appliance connections tested for gas leaks. Any leak classified under the Gas Industry Unsafe Situations Procedure and addressed before we leave.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Flue integrity and combustion spillage</strong><p>All flues tested for integrity and safe discharge. Back boilers and open-flue gas fires receive a combustion spillage test to confirm combustion products are not entering the room, this is legally required for open-flue appliances.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Ventilation adequacy</strong><p>All gas appliances checked for adequate ventilation. Particularly important for gas fires and back boilers in older WA10 terraces where ventilation is often inadequate or blocked.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Safety device operation</strong><p>All appliance safety devices tested individually. Flame failure devices on gas fires are tested. Each must demonstrate correct operation before the appliance can pass the inspection.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Signs of incomplete combustion</strong><p>Checked for staining, sooting or carbon deposits. Particularly important for gas fires and back boilers in enclosed living room settings where CO risk is higher than for sealed flue boilers.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>All gas appliances in the property</strong><p>Every gas appliance inspected individually, boiler, back boiler, gas fires, gas hobs, cookers. All recorded separately on the CP12. No appliance missed.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>CP12 certificate issued and emailed same day</strong><p>Digital CP12 emailed the same day. Includes the engineer's Gas Safe registration number, inspection date and result for every appliance checked.</p></div></div>
